kw.name: Open Browser
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to the given ``url``.

kw.name: Given Wait Until Page Contains Element
kw.doc: Waits until element ``locator`` appears on current page.

kw.name: And steps.I write and press Key
Wait Until Page Contains Element
kw.doc: Waits until element ``locator`` appears on current page.

kw.name: Input Text
kw.doc: Types the given ``text`` into text field identified by ``locator``.
kw.msg: Typing text 'deneme' into text field '//input[contains(@placeholder,'What needs to be done')]'.

kw.name: Press Keys
kw.doc: Simulates user pressing key(s) to an element or on the active browser.
kw.msg: Sending key(s) ('ENTER',) to //input[contains(@placeholder,'What needs to be done')] element.
Pressing special key ENTER to element.

kw.name: Then sleep
kw.doc: Pauses the test executed for the given time.

kw.name: Close All Browsers
kw.doc: Closes all open browsers and resets the browser cache.
